## 7. Current Core Wardrobe Inventory

*   **Bottoms:** [List what you already own so Outfitd avoids duplicating it]
*   **Tops:** [e.g., "Navy polo (Brand X), White tee (Brand Y), Olive button-down (Brand Z)."]

## 8. Generation Rules for Outfitd Agents

1.  **[Rule 1]:** [e.g., "Never recommend rigid non-stretch pants — always require elastane or an athletic cut."]
2.  **[Rule 2]:** [e.g., "No graphic tees or logo-heavy items."]
3.  **[Rule 3]:** [e.g., "Color contrast rule: don't pair a dark top with dark bottoms unless one is a neutral."]
4.  **[Rule 4]:** [e.g., "Keep tops under $80 and bottoms under $130. Prefer premium brands on sale over fast fashion at retail."]
